description: Fixes a bug where parameters passed to resource collections could be mutated after the collections were created.
[``botocore``] Update ses client to latest version
[``botocore``] Moved the JSONFileCache from the CLI into botocore so that it can be used without importing from the cli.

Update dependency strategy to always take a floor on the most recent version of ``botocore``. This means whenever there is a release of ``botocore``, ``boto3`` will release as well to account for the new version of ``botocore``.
[``botocore``] Update apigateway client to latest version
